NEWS file for ptyopen -*- outline -*-

* Changes in 0.95.

** Updated autoconf/automake build system.
** Modernized C (remove K&R prototypes).
** Show git revision in --version.
** Compiles cleanly with gcc 14.
** Provide HTML and PDF versions of the manpage.
** Provide RPM spec file.

* Changes in 0.94.

** Fixed a controlling tty problem on SysV systems.

Earlier releases of ptyopen did not set the controlling terminal
correctly on SysV systems (lacking a TIOCSCTTY ioctl).
